			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Just a note:<BR>
<BR>
If you're in a multi-layered dungeon (IE: Unrest) and you don't want a MASSIVE train..<BR>
<BR>
DO NOT CAST THIS SPELL!<BR>
<BR>
It would appear that the &quot;Area&quot; is more like a &quot;volume&quot; of effect (in this case, a sphere).  I have created HUGE trains with this spell by agro'ing things above and below me (hags, Skel monks, Barbed Bones very nasty to level 19)  <BR>
<BR>
On the other side, if you're TRYING to create a massive train (IE Guild Raids, GM events, general havoc, etc) GO TO and Good Luck to ye!<BR>
<BR>
Bofar Alestitch<BR>
24th Drinking Session Cleric<BR>
Torvinonilous
