				This spell is by no means useless.  Like any other spell it's a matter of finding the right time to use it.  This saved my party the other night.  We were swarmed by Sarnaks by the mudhole in OT and it wasn't looking good.  We had them down pretty weak but several of my comrades were down to their last 2 bubs of health.  I was trying to decide who needed my last couple of heals when decided to try this spell.  I cast it twice, the first taking out 2 flunkies and the next one took out the 3 conscripts.  My party could not believe what I had done and since then I no longer get the &quot;just heal&quot; lectures.
