	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This spell is a waste of time for Clerics, as we should really only be involved in Melee combat as a last resort at this level, but also because the mana/damage ratio is useless.  I mean, it costs 85 mana to cast &amp; does around 50ish points of damage to any monsters in a pretty small area around u.  You are better off nuking 1 monster with Strike instead for 75+, or preferably healing up the tanks so they can deal with the mob.<BR>
Anyway, u really need to get jumped by more than 3 monsters to make this anywhere near mana effective &amp; if u r soloing u should really be running away in that situation anyway, because u will have trouble casting &amp; tanking more than 2 or 3 is not a good idea for a soloing Cleric.<BR>
<BR>
Anyway this is just my humble opinion :-)<BR>
Shinarae, 20th level Cleric.
				</font>
			</td>

